reviewText: Me encant y lleg a tiempo
This was a great movie to see
Carmen Villalobos is great as usual but then it got boring.

Great show, very interesting and exciting, but I'm only giving it 4 stars because the DVD has no subtitles, not even in Spanish. It makes it hard for me to get friends that don't speak Spanish interested in it.
Good plot but still waiting to get part 2. To have a definitive opinion, I will recommend it it is good
